item.dc:creator: @Sir_wootness Sir wootness
item.description:
@Sir_wootness wrote:

Find the unpackedshops.java and edit it there, save it then find packedshops.s and delete it
then compile it just for shits and giggles but you really dont have to and done. the prices or quantity are now changed. also you can edit what the currency is here too its going to be the second number right after the shop id ex: 1 995 true, its the 995 for coins.

For example I have Zenith 711 so mine is in Zenith/data/items yours should be too.
